acne?” So... I guess its time

00:00:23.160 --> 00:00:27.130
to explain the terms that are used for the
different acne BUMPS and spots

00:00:27.130 --> 00:00:32.439
that almost everyone gets. Today I'll explain
“papules, pustules, and

00:00:32.439 --> 00:00:36.210
cysts”, and in the next episode on the language
of acne, I'll explain

00:00:36.210 --> 00:00:42.920
blackheads, whiteheads, red marks, brown marks,
